<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: MICROSOFT AND THE MEDIATOR
 &HT;    Moving in (k) commentary and (f) financial categories for
release Sunday, Dec. 12.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
