   ENTERTAINMENT/ARTS
</P>
<P>
   AIDA-REVIEW _ CHICAGO _ Theater review from Chicago of Elton
John and Tim Rice's ``Aida,'' the Disney production that is
Broadway bound and has been overhauled since its troubled Atlanta
debut in fall 1998. (Hulbert, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 22.
WITH PHOTO (of Chicago cast, the one that will likely go to
Broadway).
