Flesh,'' ``Maius and Jeannete'' and ``Trippin.''' (Staff, Cox News
Service) Art includes an 18-pica color photo from ``Deep Blue
Sea.''
</P>
<P>
   CD REVIEWS _ ``S&AMP;M,'' Metallica's 2-CD stocking stuffer of a
concept album, is a ``with strings'' adaptation of the Metallica
songbook that exploits the band's overt Wagnerian tendencies to
maximum effect. What's surprising is that it actually makes perfect
sense. Also reviews of the latest from Faith Hill and Enrique
Iglesias. (Staff, Cox News Service) Art includes 6-pica color photo
of Faith Hill. Art includes one 6-pica color photo of Faith Hill.
