   STAR FILE _ Pop superstar Billy Joel is on the road singing all
his old hits. Enjoy 'em while you can -- Joel says it's probably
the last time. (Longino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes
one 6-pica color photo of Billy Joel.
</P>
