   WHITNEY-ARTISTS _ The prestigious Whitney Biennial art exhibit
has long been notorious for featuring, and favoring, artists in
N.Y. in L.A. Now four Atlanta artists have been invited for the
March 2000 show. A look at how they were chosen, why they were
chosen and what it means. (Fox, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
MOVED. WITH PHOTOS.
</P>
