   REVIEW-MILE _ Movie review: ``The Green Mile'' starring Tom
Hanks as a prison guard who is mesmerized by a huge convicted
murderer (who may be innocent) and who has strange mystical powers.
Grade: B+ (Murray, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
