<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-09 14:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4196 &Cx1f; tab-z
r l BC-TREND-WATCH-MILLENNIU     12-09 0178
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TREND-WATCH-MILLENNIUM-NYTSF </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Surprise your teen this holiday season by being ahead of the
gift-giving curve. Find out what's really hot this holiday season.
Are you wise to:
</P>
<P>
   STICKER JEWELRY
</P>
<P>
   TOO-FACED LIP-GLOSS RINGS
</P>
<P>
   SOAP SHOES
</P>
<P>
   CUSTARD BAGS
</P>
<P>
   RIO and
</P>
<P>
   SWIFFER?
</P>
<P>
   What's neXt? Decode your curiosity by subscribing to neXt.
</P>
<P>
   Want a peek at the future? Subscribe to neXt, the new weekly
column on youth trends by Jane Rinzler Buckingham. Her company,
Youth Intelligence, tracks the opinions and habits of the under-30
crowd. Her column reveals what's hot, what's not _ and why _ in
fashion, food, entertainment, activities and more.
</P>
<P>
   Every column includes a ``Trend Watch'' box. And every editor
who subscribes to neXt will receive valuable marketing information
