<P>
   KING-FAMILY _ ATLANTA _ Follow on King verdict _ including
coverage of press conference at King center. In addition, we'll
look at the King family's changing role in the civil rights
community and where this lawsuit and the result fit. (Suggs,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). WITH PHOTO.
