u a BC-CDC-HIV10-COX     12-09 0477
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CDC-HIV10-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SCIENCE/HEALTH: Use names for tracking AIDS virus, CDC urges
 &HT;    By Patricia Guthrie
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
