   &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; OPTIONS _ &LR;  Despite the stories of stock option millionaires, the
truth is the majority of high-tech workers in the Bay Area actually
saw their dreams of vast wealth wane with the demise of their
