<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-09 23:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4881 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u e BC-VIDEO-REVIEWS-HNS &LR;      12-09 0871
